Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所属不明的穿梭机\N正前来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机?
