Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，多次呼唤也没回覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发出指示叫警备队紧守防卫线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.97,0:03:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是OZ第一部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告接近中的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上改变航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再接近\N我们就会开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是恐吓，是警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管，开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近中的飞行物体爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变型了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击!攻击攻击!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士中弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去平衡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是钢弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种攻击根本不能击倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说我天真吗?技师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再倚靠他们的力量会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和钢弹有关的人还有利用价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在把麦丘留士操纵自如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遗憾，OZ的驾驶员里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无人的技术能超越他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，太危险了
