Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们现在不能轻举妄动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特和麦丘留士量产型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生产准备在月面基地那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在照预定计划进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经不需要他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何讨厌他们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫉妒吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种感情我不敢恭维啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡说!我为何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!有紧急联络进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,07U1地点的资源卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以往的资料里没有的新钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星和发现它的部队一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被钢弹消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.26,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么你为何知道\N那是钢弹的所为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是敌人驾驶员的人有通讯来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他宣布跟着会消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,06E地点的民间卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及送来相信是不能到手的
