Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派MD陶拉斯出击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD不能调离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地的防守岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派拜叶特和麦丘留士出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特和麦丘留士的破坏力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在比陶拉斯优胜
