Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与推动时代的和平对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来有事发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相当惊徨
