Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身份不明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是新机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特征呢?武器呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么详细情报吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,04，好像和沙漠钢弹有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔吗?
