Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.25,0:08:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能完全毁灭资源卫星的破坏力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在去确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的把卫星毁灭了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看资源卫星的规模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但预测破坏力\N就要看它的设计图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他造出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们五人研究的钢弹的原型吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点危险的气息啊
