Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他装上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道?还是失控了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在做连我们也犹豫的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.12,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一两个卫星真的会被毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来，1号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，又是1号吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2号比1号优良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我应付今次的对手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那身体状况做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的驾驶员今次或许也会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为对手是钢弹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是新机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一部就令OZ的部队全军覆没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特征呢?武器呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是执行任务的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题和技师们的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它和那部叫\N麦丘留士的红色家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会旗鼓相当吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想来也要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫钢弹驾驶员自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你就坐山观虎门吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，1号，不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是机动战士的性能测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要帮手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们乖乖地不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚会轮到你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是挖空心思的戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也须要提防他已经是敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用那么担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他能信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为出卖我们的人不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带这种巧妙的东西来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有张五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师O把这个交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用它来解闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特和麦丘留士的运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两部机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.95,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧和五飞的钢弹被改良了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而新的钢弹一定是卡特尔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时机或许来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和卡特尔会合后就反击OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何能断定他是自己人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推测会产生错误啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我们现在驾驶OZ的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据情况也可能会战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是强大的自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就能如你所言反击OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那部钢弹\N只有轻微的攻击力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就毁灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潜伏在OZ的你在收拾特列斯前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隐藏你的身份是优先的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你一直知道的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样也好，战斗看看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平民避难完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人从哪里出现也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防守别松懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一区正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二区正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个卫星装有外部雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何敌人来袭也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个卫星能保卫自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星06E3注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要毁灭卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止无谓的反抗，马上撤离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，马上撤离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎击!外部雷射炮准备发射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，不要战斗就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.93,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪啊，我在流泪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我毫不伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那卫星已经无法挽救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说接着会毁灭这空域的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用运输机前去太引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由这里起用机动战士移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是确认钢弹的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，有需要时就战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但对手是卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用杞人忧天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，小心行事，有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他…把卫星毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们引开敌人的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麦丘留士单独行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它一出现就毁灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太放任前钢弹驾驶员自由行动了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它自爆装置的开关在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.65,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而现在\N他的眼里只是看见钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他会清楚看见敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻一个月后完成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔也行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又会忙起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会把...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.81,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身份不明的机动战士为自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那部钢弹在消灭OZ啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是就最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.86,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容设施的空气提供系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫技师长\N你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是载断了监狱的空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有收到任何指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有蕾蒂‧安特校的批准吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,批准由我来下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是遵从正确的指示啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.73,0:17:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安小姐太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，年纪有点大了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双脚站不稳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，那是缺氧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你发觉了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你操心才那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想让你老人家担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有30分钟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遣憾的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.88,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神和神龙的改良还未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想死的人就快点去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别浪费空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顽强的老人会被讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生不顽强就不能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶…他想我们死得安心点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.64,0:17:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日毕竟由我代希洛出击就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么?五飞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今，那种东西有等于没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想活得久一点，你就别出声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.42,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但没有奇蹟发生\N我们就死定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是为了有奇蹟发生的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做现在能做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我现在要退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.20,0:18:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没出息的死法，我真丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外部看来没有动态反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它真的在这种地方吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会已经去了其他空域吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会，钢弹一定在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星不需要这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里!是钢弹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在卫星里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星须要的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星里的三部机被毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人钢弹出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，让我看吧
